title: Navarro cousins lead Stayton to Oregon West soccer victory
text: Navarro cousins lead Stayton to Oregon West soccer victory Bill Poehler , Statesman Journal 7:28 p.m. PDT October 20, 2015 Buy Photo Stayton's Ivan Navarro (10) fights for the ball with North Marion's Jair Cano (14) and Oscar Ruiz-Contreras (2) in the Stayton vs. North Marion boy's soccer game at North Marion High School in Aurora, Ore., on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015. Stayton won the game 3-2.
